org.apache.flink.table.store.format

Class FileFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.table.store.format.FileFormat
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AvroFileFormat, OrcFileFormat, ParquetFileFormat

    public abstract class FileFormat
extends Object
    Factory class which creates reader and writer factories for specific file format.

    NOTE: This class must be thread safe.
